# --- eval (Phase 9): Microsoft.Extensions.AI.Evaluation disk store + cache + generated reports ---
# Datasets under eval/datasets/ ARE committed (versioned JSON); the disk result store / response cache
# and the dotnet aieval HTML report are local artifacts (the queryable store is RLS Postgres).
eval/.report-store/
eval/*.html
